org.universAAL.ucc.configuration.model

Class ConfigOptionRegistry

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.universAAL.ucc.configuration.model.ConfigOptionRegistry

  • public class ConfigOptionRegistry
extends Object
    The registry class to manage the configuration options. Every configuration option adds itself to this registry. You can ask the registry for configuration options by its id's.
    Author:
    Sebastian.Schoebinge
